What is javascript?

javascript is high level and a core technologies of web alongside HTML and CSS. it is use on both client and server side.

Uses of javascript.
1. DOM manipulation
2. Event handling
3. Asynchronous reavests
4. Data manipulation (sorting,filtering etc)
5. Storing data (cookies, local storage etc)
6. Single page application(SPA)
7. Creating Apis and web services (nodejs ,deno)

Reason to learn javascript
1. popularity
2. versatility
3. relatively easy to learn
4. join community

Environmental setup
1. vs code
2. git
3. node.js
4. live server
5. prettier

